HEADWORD: Alcedo
<hw>Al*ce"do</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., equiv. to
Gr. <?/. See <er>Halcyon</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of
